version_description: Tabbed for acoustic guitar. Currently, there does not seem to be other versions with lyrics and chords.

song_name: The Last Of The Unplucked Gems
version_description: Tabs and chords to Last of the Unplucked Gems.
This version was created to play on an acoustic guitar. The chords have been changed from Version 1. In addition, the chords have been put above each lyric for ease of use.

The strumming is a little unique so you're going to have to listen to the song to get it down correctly. It also seems like the chords don't line up to the lyrics for things like the chorus and the bridge, but the way he sings changes slightly so the chords are shifted every now and then.

Added Tab for the opening riff, showed chord progression all the way through the song to the end. Indicated where full stops and chord accents occur. I feel it is a more accurate interpretation of the actual song as heard on the original track.
This is based on the acoustic outtake version from the demo Alex Chilton sessions.
